\alpha,\beta,\gamma\in\mathbb{R}
|\alpha+\beta-\gamma|+|\alpha+\gamma-\beta|+|\beta+\gamma-\alpha|\ge|\alpha|+|\beta|+|\gamma|
\alpha,\beta,\gamma>0
\alpha+\beta\ge\gamma
\alpha+\beta\le\gamma
|\alpha +\beta - \gamma|+|\alpha + \gamma - \beta| \geq |\alpha +\beta - \gamma +\alpha + \gamma - \beta|=2|\alpha|
